name: Nelson Enterprise Technology Services
overview:
Nelson Enterprise Technology Services (NETS) is an emerging Service Disabled Veteran Owned and Minority Owned Small Business providing IT infrastructure Support, Systems Engineering and Network Engineering Enterprise professional services to the Federal, State and Local Governments.

NETS is a highly skilled team of Engineers that aim to provide high quality professional Systems and Network Enterprise Professional services with an emphasis on Next Gen technologies.

NETS offers solutions to meet the challenging requirements in e-Business, e-Government, e-Health, Networks, Communication and Management. We are an emerging technology firm on the forefront of new and innovative solutions that continually improve services.
